      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The thought that your absence would somehow make things easier is a clear sign of how much pain you are in right now. It's a twisted logic born from exhaustion, but it doesn't mean you are anything less than a valuable person. Please reach out to a crisis line immediately; they are trained to help you through these intense feelings without judgment. You deserve support, and there are people who want to help you navigate this.",
      "source": "target",
